videos.description: Memphis' Jeremiah Martin gets the steal and passes to Dedric Lawson for the layup.
videos.headline: Memphis steal leads to  Lawson layup

videos.description: Memphis' Dedrick Lawsoon blocks the shot and Craig Randall finds Markel Crawford for the layup on the fast break.
videos.headline: Memphis blocks the shot and it leads to  Crawford layup
